      "text": "",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771809318,
      "updated": 1771809318
    },
    {
      "id": "699baa270000000000aa6425",
      "text": "[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771809318,
      "updated": 1771809320
    },
    {
      "id": "699baa2a0000000000aa6426",
      "text": " 今日休みでいいんだよな、、とカレンダーを確認する",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771809321,
      "updated": 1771809337
    },
    {
      "id": "699baa3a0000000000aa6427",
      "text": "  いつもの儀式",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771809337,
      "updated": 1771809344
    },
    {
      "id": "699baa410000000000aa6428",
      "text": " 喫茶店でホットケーキを食べる",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771809344,
      "updated": 1771809358
    },
    {
      "id": "699baa4f0000000000aa6429",
      "text": "  懐かしい感じ",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771809358,
      "updated": 1771809364
    },
    {
      "id": "699baa570000000000aa642a",
      "text": "  子供の頃しか食べてなかった",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771809366,
      "updated": 1771809379
    },
    {
      "id": "699baae80000000000aa642b",
      "text": " obsidian cli 良さげ",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771809512,
      "updated": 1771809522
    },
    {
      "id": "699baaf30000000000aa642c",
      "text": "  「今開いてるページ」を認識してくれそう←LLMに読み書きさせられそう",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771809522,
      "updated": 1771809557
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd93b0000000000b27dfc",
      "text": "  この発想いいなぁ[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1771821373,
      "updated": 1771821377
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd9510000000000b27dfd",
      "text": "  \t名前つけて捉えとこ: [Current Focus Context]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1771821395,
      "updated": 1771821403
    },
