      "updated": 1771818352
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd15e0000000000a649fa",
      "text": "  試験勉強累計634時間まできてた。結構すごいよね。応援したい[hoshihara.icon]",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1771819359,
      "updated": 1771819393
    },
    {
      "id": "699db55e0000000000d1beaa",
      "text": "   先が長すぎる[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1771943263,
      "updated": 1771943311
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd5e50000000000b27dfa",
      "text": " \t[基素.icon]さんに担当してもらうことや、[はるひ.icon]さんに診察してもらうことは俺の夢の一つかもしれない[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1771820519,
      "updated": 1771820566
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd61c0000000000b27dfb",
      "text": " \t\t熱い展開",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1771820573,
      "updated": 1771820575
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd9cc000000000055fdda",
      "text": " \t\tこれはアツい[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771821515,
      "updated": 1771821519
    },
    {
      "id": "699bdf6100000000005cb3c5",
      "text": " \t\t[井戸端アベンジャーズ]だ[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771822945,
      "updated": 1771833334
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd82d0000000000170c59",
      "text": " \t[加油.icon][caki.icon][takker.icon][taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771821101,
      "updated": 1771891159
    },
    {
      "id": "699bcae000000000002a0c65",
      "text": "  ちな敗北[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1771817697,
      "updated": 1771943250
    },
    {
      "id": "699db54e0000000000d1bea9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1771943247,
      "updated": 1771943247
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd1d000000000000f8c37",
      "text": "[hoshihara.icon]",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1771819472,
      "updated": 1771819474
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd1d000000000000f8c38",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1771819472,
      "updated": 1771819472
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd9610000000000170c5a",
      "text": "[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771821410,
      "updated": 1771821412
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd9640000000000170c5b",
      "text": " 殻付きの胡桃を2週間ほど前に入手し、これをどうやって割るか問題とまだ向き合ってる",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771821412,
      "updated": 1771821479
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd9890000000000170c5c",
      "text": "  諦めてくるみ割りを買うべきかもしれない",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771821449,
      "updated": 1771821462
    },
    {
      "id": "699bdf460000000000e7f08a",
      "text": "  割れるまで握って握力トレーニングに使う()[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771822918,
      "updated": 1771822942
    },
    {
      "id": "699bdf8900000000005cb3c6",
      "text": "   西洋くるみだからワンチャンありそう[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771822986,
      "updated": 1771822997
    },
    {
      "id": "699bdf5f0000000000e7f08b",
      "text": "  上から重いものを落とせば割れそう",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771822943,
      "updated": 1771822965
    },
    {
      "id": "699bdf750000000000e7f08c",
      "text": "  　コンクリートの上に置いて、50cmくらいの高さから1kg~2.5kg程度の重りを落とす",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771822965,
      "updated": 1771822997
    },
    {
      "id": "699bdf9e0000000000e7f08d",
      "text": "  　[- 中身が粉砕する可能性は考慮しないものとする]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771823005,
      "updated": 1771823023
    },
    {
      "id": "699be27900000000005cb3c7",
      "text": "  　ダンベルで叩くといけるかも[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771823737,
      "updated": 1771823758
    },
    {
      "id": "699be2b300000000005cb3c9",
      "text": "  　 他の部屋の人からの苦情もセットで来るかも",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771823796,
      "updated": 1771823811
    },
    {
      "id": "699bf9480000000000a4e103",
      "text": " CLAUDE.md等のプロンプトの中にコメントを書きたい",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771829576,
      "updated": 1771829610
    },
    {
      "id": "699c061d0000000000e80786",
      "text": " オモコロの絵心オセロからの流れでジェスチャーオセロを見たらたまに話に出る原宿さんの虹が見れた",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771832862,
      "updated": 1771832910
    },
    {
      "id": "699c064e0000000000e80787",
      "text": "  [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8q-xot_l15U&t=1032s&pp=0gcJCTAAlc8ueATH]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771832910,
      "updated": 1771832912
    },
    {
      "id": "699c06500000000000e80788",
      "text": "   思ったよりも虹だった",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771832912,
      "updated": 1771832921
    },
    {
      "id": "699c084100000000008a4d8d",
      "text": " 昨日の教訓をいかせず、今日も花粉症の薬を飲みわすれた",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771833409,
      "updated": 1771833430
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd9980000000000170c5d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771821464,
      "updated": 1771821465
    },
    {
      "id": "699be50500000000005c114c",
      "text": "[hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1771824390,
      "updated": 1771824396
    },
    {
      "id": "699be50c00000000005c114e",
      "text": " [イル・バーニ — ヒッタイト語教室 https://ilbani.com/]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1771824396,
      "updated": 1771824401
    },
    {
      "id": "699be50500000000005c114d",
      "text": " \t結構ガチなサイトだった",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1771824390,
      "updated": 1771824407
    },
    {
      "id": "699be51a00000000005c1150",
      "text": " \tいつかやる(願望)",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1771824410,
      "updated": 1771824422
    },
    {
      "id": "699c17ec000000000064ef57",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1771837420,
      "updated": 1771837420
    },
    {
      "id": "699c17ec000000000064ef58",
      "text": "[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1771837420,
      "updated": 1771837422
    },
    {
      "id": "699c1b0d000000000064ef5b",
      "text": "　サルにパンチって名前つけるのはしっくり来る事だ",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1771838222,
      "updated": 1771838230
    },
    {
      "id": "699c17ee000000000064ef59",
      "text": "　[ブゴニア]を見に行くのがおすすめ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771837423,
      "updated": 1771837725
    },
    {
      "id": "699be50e00000000005c114f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1771824399,
      "updated": 1771824399
    },
    {
      "id": "699c2bd200000000000da290",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771842515,
      "updated": 1771842516
    },
    {
      "id": "699c2e7400000000000da297",
      "text": "\tよくわからない語彙",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771843188,
      "updated": 1771843195
    },
    {
      "id": "699c2bd400000000000da292",
      "text": " \t語彙クラスタA",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771842516,
      "updated": 1771843197
    },
    {
      "id": "699c2bea00000000000da293",
      "text": "  \tつけいる、侮る（あなどる）、ナメられる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771842538,
      "updated": 1771843197
    },
    {
      "id": "699c2d7800000000000da296",
      "text": " \t語彙クラスタB",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771842937,
      "updated": 1771843197
    },
    {
      "id": "699c2c0f00000000000da294",
      "text": "  \t調子に乗る、粋がる、イキる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771842575,
      "updated": 1771843197
    },
    {
      "id": "699c2d3800000000000da295",
      "text": "  \t自惚（うぬぼ）れる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771842872,
      "updated": 1771843197
    },
    {
      "id": "699c3b9200000000000da298",
      "text": " 上下関係に関する語彙の理解が薄い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771846546,
      "updated": 1771846566
    },
    {
      "id": "699c3bb100000000000da299",
      "text": " \tと言うよりも、上下関係というものへの理解が薄い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771846578,
      "updated": 1771847121
    },
    {
      "id": "699c3c2f00000000000da29a",
      "text": " \tと言うよりも、上下関係というものへの理解を拒絶している",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771846704,
      "updated": 1771846719
    },
    {
      "id": "699c3dda00000000000da29b",
      "text": " \tと言うよりも、下から見ることへの理解を拒絶している",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771847130,
      "updated": 1771847166
    },
    {
      "id": "699c3e1400000000000da29c",
      "text": " \t単にプライドが（悪い意味で）高い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771847188,
      "updated": 1771847204
    },
    {
      "id": "699c420400000000000da29d",
      "text": " 上を見た時に理由に納得がいく時には気が済むが、納得いかない時にとにかく反発する",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771848197,
      "updated": 1771848620
    },
    {
      "id": "699c43b400000000000da29e",
      "text": " \t弱みだねぇ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771848628,
      "updated": 1771848804
    },
    {
      "id": "699c452000000000000da29f",
      "text": " \t人に学ぶのが難しいので難儀する",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771848993,
      "updated": 1771849023
    },
    {
      "id": "699c455100000000000da2a0",
      "text": " \t[\" 納得いかない時にとにかく反発する]ということは、未知領域の学習に難儀する",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771849042,
      "updated": 1771849197
    },
    {
      "id": "699c46ca00000000000da2a2",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771849418,
      "updated": 1771849922
    },
    {
      "id": "699c485900000000000da2a4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771849817,
      "updated": 1771849841
    },
